title: StartTutorial
position: -844,-966
---
Hello, Soldier. How are the preparations for the meeting going?
    -> Hello, Colonel. Everything is ready. We await the attendees.

Good. Unfortunately we've received information that PIDE agents might try to infiltrate the meeting.
    -> (Continue)

They will try to impersonate the attendees, so you'll have to double-check everyone’s identities.
    -> Yes, Colonel. But how should I do that?
        <<jump BeginTutorial>>
    -> Yes, Colonel. You can count on me!
        <<set $jumpedTutorial = true>>
        <<jump EndTutorial>>

===

